se out of a tink bag when i hit it, so that the weight penalty drops my AC so that the NPC will get more hits in that i can turn around and toss back. and on the same theory of use a high dmg weapon w/ autoriposte, if its a trick you intend to use often, get double riposte and riposte kick. especially against enrage, you'll just keep multiplying the ripostes. great fun, tons o spam. <p><hr><center><table><tr><td align=center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=8143">Talynn Raijinken</a><br>
